(firstQuint)Pressure and Temperature Sensor for Therapeutic Compression Garments.

 Assessment of safety, and preliminary accuracy of a pressure and temperature sensor adherent to the skin.

 The pressure sensor includes a piezoresistive fabric coupled to a near-field communication chip with a built-in temperature sensor.

